FuncDef: This command specifies E-3 framing for the associated E-3 port or channel.

ParaDef.Info: Configures the E-3 port/channel for g751 framing.
Configures the E-3 port/channel for g832 framing.
Specifies e-3 unframed mode for E-3 interfaces. This parameter allows the configuration of an unstructured E-3 channel on a CES MDA.

ExtraInfo:
Default: for E-3 non-ATM:	 framing g751 and cannot be changed.
for E-3 ATM: 	framing g832 and cannot be changed.
